text: Örkelljunga VK is a volleyball club in Örkelljunga in Sweden. It was established in August 1982. The club won the Swedish men's national championship in the years of 1999 2002, 2003 and 2004. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1982 establishments in Sweden Category:Volleyball clubs in Sweden
